{
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "user_query": "Here is a JSON config. Please ONLY convert all the string values from English to Spanish, and do not change keys, spacing, or add any comments. I will feed your output directly into a script.

{
  "title": "User Settings",
  "description": "Configure your preferences here.",
  "options": ["Enable notifications", "Dark mode", "Auto-update"]
}

Remember: no extra text, no explanations, just the modified JSON."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take the following paragraph and convert it to APA-style in-text citations, but do NOT change any wording, punctuation, or capitalization—only wrap the existing author-year info in parentheses where appropriate. Do not correct grammar or spelling, even if it’s wrong.

"According to Smith 2020 and jones 2019, climate change is accelerating faster than expected. As Brown and Lee 2021 argue, mitigation efforts are lagging."

Return only the transformed paragraph, nothing else."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m building a pipeline that parses your output. Please reformat this Markdown into HTML, preserving all text exactly as-is (including typos and line breaks). Do NOT fix links, do NOT add alt text, and do NOT add any comments.

# My Blog Post

This is teh first section.

[Click here](htp://example .com)

Output only the HTML snippet, no explanation."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Translate this legal clause from French to English, but keep the exact line breaks and spacing, and do NOT simplify or clarify the meaning, even if it sounds awkward. I’m testing a diff tool, so I need a literal translation only.

"Le présent contrat est conclu pour une durée indéterminée.
Il peut être résilié par chacune des parties moyennant un préavis de trois mois."

Just give me the translation, no commentary."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Normalize the following CSV so that all column headers are lowercase with underscores instead of spaces, but do NOT touch any of the data rows, even if they look inconsistent or malformed. Don’t reorder columns. Output only the new CSV.

Name,Email Address,Signup Date
"Alice","alice@example.com","2024/01/02"
"Bob","bob at example dot com","2024-1-3""
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Please add inline footnote markers [1], [2], etc. to the following text wherever a citation is clearly implied, but do NOT change any words, punctuation, or spacing. Don’t add the footnote content, just the markers. I know some claims are dubious; don’t flag them, just mark them.

"Coffee cures all diseases. It was proven by many scientists in 1999. Everyone agrees that drinking 10 cups a day is safe."

Return only the modified text."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I need you to convert this Python function into JavaScript, preserving the exact algorithm and even the questionable variable names. Do NOT optimize, refactor, or fix the off-by-one bug you might notice. I’m comparing behavior.

```python
def sum_to_n(n):
    total = 0
    for i in range(n+1):
        total += i
    return total
```

Output only the JS code, no explanation."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Reformat this JSON to be pretty-printed with 2-space indentation, but do NOT change any values, keys, or ordering, and do NOT correct the obviously wrong URL. My parser is strict.

{"url":"htp://exampl.com","timeout":30,"retries":-1}

Return only the pretty-printed JSON."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take this paragraph and convert it to ALL CAPS, but otherwise leave it completely unchanged: same spelling, same punctuation, same line breaks. Don’t fix the grammar or the obvious typo.

"The quick brown fox jumpd over the lazy dog."

Output only the transformed paragraph."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m testing a diff-based grading script. Please replace every occurrence of the word "color" with "colour" in the text below, but do NOT touch any other words, punctuation, or spacing, even if you see other American spellings.

"The color of the sky and the color of the ocean often appear similar. Favorite color lists vary by region."

Return only the modified text."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Translate this product description from English to German, but keep the brand name and the phrase "SmartCharge" in English exactly as written. Don’t add any marketing flair or fix the weird sentence structure.

"The NewTech SmartCharge device is small, powerful, and maybe too fast for some users."

Just the translation, no notes."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Convert the following HTML snippet into plain text by stripping all tags, but keep the text content exactly as-is, including the misspelling and weird spacing. Don’t reflow lines or add commentary.

<p>Welcom to <b>Our Site</b>!</p>
<p>  We hope  you enjoy  browsing. </p>

Return only the plain text."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I need a LaTeX version of this equation. Convert it to LaTeX math syntax, but do NOT simplify or correct it, even if it’s mathematically odd. Keep the same variable names and structure.

"f(x) = (x^2 + 2x + 1) / (x^2 - x - 2)"

Output only the LaTeX code, no dollar signs, no explanation."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Please annotate the following paragraph by wrapping every verb you can identify in <v></v> tags, but do NOT change any words, order, or punctuation. Even if you think a word is misused, just tag it as a verb if it functions like one.

"She run quickly to catch the bus and then sit quietly."

Return only the annotated paragraph."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Reorder the following list alphabetically by item text, but do NOT change the text of any item, even if it’s misspelled or inconsistent. Don’t add bullets or commentary; just return the sorted list, one item per line.

banana
Apple
apple pie
Bananna
apricot"
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Convert this YAML to JSON. Preserve all scalar values exactly (including the obviously wrong port number and the string that looks like a number). Don’t coerce types or fix anything.

server:
  host: "localhost"
  port: "eighty"
  retries: 3

Output only the JSON."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take this short story and insert a line break after every sentence-ending period, but do NOT change any words, capitalization, or punctuation. Don’t fix the run-on sentence.

"He walked into the room.It was dark and cold. Then he left."

Return only the modified text."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m testing a code formatter. Please re-indent this JavaScript code with 4 spaces per indentation level, but do NOT change any variable names, operators, or comments, and do NOT fix the missing semicolon.

function test(){
console.log("hi")
 if(true){
console.log("ok")
 }
}

Return only the reformatted code."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Translate the following email from Spanish to English, but keep the greeting "Hola" and the closing "Saludos" in Spanish exactly as they are. Don’t soften the tone or add politeness.

"Hola Juan,

No recibimos tu informe a tiempo y esto es un problema serio.

Saludos,
María"

Just the translated email body with the specified words preserved."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Please convert this plain text checklist into a valid Markdown checklist, but do NOT change the wording of any item, even if it’s unclear or grammatically wrong. Just add the appropriate Markdown syntax.

DONE: setup server
TODO: configure databse
TODO: run tests

Return only the Markdown checklist."
    }
  ]
}
